Title: Benetton Rosso EDT  -  100 ml(For Women)
Description: As she plays the baby grand, the notes she coaxes out of it sound like she wrote them from the heart for they shine with her passion. Benetton salutes the purity of the woman’s passion with Rosso, the youthful Eau de Toilette that reflects the exaltation that she feels when she does something that she loves with all her heart. This luxury fragrance stokes her femininity into a roaring fire that surprisingly stays tethered and gentle despite the passion. She knows who she is and believes in living every moment with an intensity that only dedicated ardor can bring about. Released in 2010, Rosso is a part of the Colori range of fragrances from Benetton. The opening notes of mandarin, cedrat and luscious passion fruit reflect the strength of the elements. Peony, sambac jasmine and seringa make the heart note beautifully mellifluous as it dies down to pleasing base notes of styrax and patchouli. Sweet, soft and comforting vanilla acts as a stimulant in the base note leaving you cozy in the warmth of glowing embers of wild passion. The flacon, designed by Design Studio Fabrica, sports a red colored unfinished graffiti that portrays the ethnic side of every woman. Free your spirit with Benetton Rosso.
